## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of data and the potential biases in the sources reviewed. Many arguments for and against gun ownership are deeply rooted in ideological beliefs, which can influence the presentation of facts. Additionally, the complexity of gun laws and their enforcement varies significantly across different jurisdictions, which may not be fully captured in this analysis. Further research could include more empirical studies and data-driven analyses to provide a more comprehensive understanding of the impacts of gun ownership on society.